The title template controls how thread or announcement titles will appear when items are posted.<br />
<br />
You may use any node from the feed XML by entering {feed:<strong>x</strong>} into the template, where 'x' corresponds to:
<ul>
<li>title</li>
<li>description</li>
<li>link</li>
<li>id</li>
<li>date</li>
<li>enclosure_href</li>
<li>content:encoded.</li>
</ul>
<br />
For the most part, you will use {feed:title} to show the title for the current feed item.